methods.slice:
Make a new Chunk that represents either exactly the same view on the underlying data as this Chunk, or a
 subrange of that view. The view is defined as [0..size) (in the coordinate space of this Chunk).

:param offset: int
:param capacity: int
:return: (io.deephaven.db.v2.sources.chunk.ResettableShortChunk) The new Chunk. A new Chunk will always be returned, even if the Chunks represent the same view.
